        How to Withdraw Your Property from Sale in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Pulling your property off the market mid-campaign is not failure. Sometimes it is the right commercial decision. Here is what it involves and what it costs.
      </p>
